The Lakers traded Derek Fisher and Adam Morrison to the Raptors for Hedo Turkoglu and a 2013 2nd round pick (TOR).
The Cavaliers traded Daniel Gibson, Danny Green, Shaquille O'Neal, a 2010 1st round pick (CLE), and a 2011 2nd round pick (CLE) to the Grizzlies for Hamed Haddadi, Allen Iverson, and Zach Randolph.
The Grizzlies traded Marc Gasol, Sam Young, a 2011 1st round pick (MEM), and a 2012 2nd round pick (MEM) to the Timberwolves for Kevin Love.
The Grizzlies traded Shaquille O'Neal to the Timberwolves for Brian Cardinal, Jason Hart, Nathan Jawai, Sasha Pavlovic, Oleksiy Pecherov, Damien Wilkins, and a 2013 2nd round pick (MIN).

The Grizzlies traded Brian Cardinal, Trey Gilder, Jason Hart, Steven Hunter, Sasha Pavlovic, Jamaal Tinsley, and Damien Wilkins to the Knicks for Eddy Curry, Jordan Hill, Jared Jeffries, a 2010 2nd round pick (NYK), and a 2011 2nd round pick (NYK).
The Nuggets traded Chris Andersen, J.R. Smith, and a 2012 1st round pick (DEN) to the Warriors for Monta Ellis.

The Jazz traded Andrei Kirilenko, Wesley Matthews, C.J. Miles, and a 2011 1st round pick (UTA) to the Nets for Devin Harris, Trenton Hassell, Courtney Lee, Brook Lopez, and a 2013 2nd round pick (NJN).
The Bulls traded Joe Alexander, Brad Miller, and Tyrus Thomas to the Rockets for Shane Battier, Yao Ming, a 2011 1st round pick (HOU), and a 2013 1st round pick (HOU).
The Bulls traded Kirk Hinrich to the Mavericks for Josh Howard.
The Trailblazers traded Greg Oden, Joel Przybilla, a 2011 2nd round pick (POR), and a 2013 1st round pick (POR) to the Bucks for Andrew Bogut.
The Trailblazers traded Nicolas Batum and Jerryd Bayless to the Warriors for Anthony Morrow, a 2011 2nd round pick (GSW), and a 2012 1st round pick (GSW).
The Bulls traded Luol Deng to the Mavericks for Drew Gooden, Tim Thomas, a 2012 1st round pick (DAL), and a 2013 1st round pick (DAL).
The Trailblazers traded Travis Outlaw, a 2012 1st round pick (POR), and a 2013 2nd round pick (POR) to the Rockets for Brad Miller and Luis Scola.
The Thunder traded Nick Collison, Serge Ibaka, a 2010 2nd round pick (OKC), and a 2013 1st round pick (OKC) to the Suns for Grant Hill and Amar'e Stoudemire.
The Rockets released Joey Dorsey.

The Bucks traded Brandon Jennings to the Clippers for Ricky Davis, a 2011 2nd round pick (LAC), a 2012 1st round pick (LAC), a 2012 2nd round pick (LAC), a 2013 1st round pick (LAC), and a 2013 2nd round pick (LAC).

The Hawks traded Maurice Evans, Jeff Teague, Marvin Williams, a 2010 1st round pick (ATL), a 2011 1st round pick (ATL), a 2011 2nd round pick (ATL), and a 2013 2nd round pick (ATL) to the Jazz for Deron Williams.
